headline: Endorsement of Keith Self
body_text: Keith Self will be a terrific Congressman for the people of Texas’ 3rd Congressional District! Keith bravely served our Country as a Lieutenant Colonel in the U.S. Army, and, in Congress, he will Strengthen our Military, Support our Veterans, Fight for Election Security, and Defend our Second Amendment, which is under siege by the Radical Left.  Keith Self has my Complete and Total Endorsement!

headline: Endorsement of Mike Collins
body_text: Mike Collins will be a fantastic Representative for the wonderful people of Georgia’s 10th Congressional District. A trucker, Mike is a very successful businessman from a tough industry who knows how to Create Jobs, Fight Inflation, and Grow our Economy.  Mike will work hard to Support our Veterans, Strengthen our Military, Defend the Second Amendment, and Stand Up to the Woke Mob that is destroying our Country. Mike Collins is an America First Conservative, and has my Complete and Total Endorsement!

headline: Save America Announces Additional Special Guest Speakers in Mesa, Arizona
body_text: President Donald J. Trump, 45th President of the United States of America, will be joined by endorsed candidates and other special guests on Sunday, October 9, 2022, in Mesa, AZ. This Save America rally is a continuation of President Trump’s unprecedented effort to advance the MAGA agenda by energizing voters and highlighting America First candidates and causes. Sunday, October 9, 2022, at 4:00PM MSTPresident Donald J. Trump, 45th President of the United States of America, delivers remarks in support of endorsed candidates and special guests Kari Lake, Republican Nominee for Governor of Arizona and Blake Masters, Republican Nominee for U.S. Senate in Arizona, and the entire Arizona Trump Ticket. Venue:Legacy Sports Park6321 S. Ellsworth RoadMesa, AZ 85212 Newly Announced Special Guest Speakers:Rep. Andy Biggs, U.S. Representative for Arizona’s 5th Congressional DistrictRep. Debbie Lesko, U.S. Representative for Arizona’s 8th Congressional DistrictRep. Marjorie Taylor Greene, U.S. Representative for Georgia’s 14th Congressional DistrictAmbassador Ric Grenell, Former Acting Director of National Intelligence and Former U.S. Ambassador to GermanyKash Patel, Former Chief of Staff to the Department of Defense for President Donald J. Trump Previously Announced Special Guest Speakers:Ms. Kari Lake, Republican Nominee for Governor of ArizonaMr. Blake Masters, Republican Nominee for U.S. Senate in ArizonaRep. Mark Finchem, Republican Nominee for Secretary of State of ArizonaMr. Abraham Hamadeh, Republican Nominee for Attorney General of Arizona Timeline of Events:7:00AM – Parking Lots, Vendor Row, and Registration Open11:00AM – Doors Open1:00PM – Special Guest Speakers Deliver Remarks4:00PM – 45th President of the United States Donald J. Trump Delivers RemarksEntertainment and Concessions will be available throughout the day! General Admission Tickets:REGISTER HERE Request Media Credentials:REGISTER HERE All requests for media credentials must be submitted by Friday, October 7, 2022, at 5:00PM MST.

headline: Statement by Donald J. Trump, 45th President of the United States of America
body_text: On top of the lost “Clinton Hard Drive,” there are also tapes from the George H.W. Bush and Ronald Reagan Administrations which were lost AFTER having been ordered preserved by a Federal Judge. Some hard drives were even “damaged by sloppy handling in the transfer”! The National Archivist actually gave George H.W. Bush "exclusive legal control over all Presidential information.” Compare that to how unfairly and illegally the 45th President, me, has been treated! Read here.

headline: Statement by Donald J. Trump, 45th President of the United States of America
body_text: NARA lost a whole hard drive full of HIGHLY SENSITIVE information from the Clinton White House—more than 100,000 Social Security numbers and addresses, Secret Service and White House operating procedures (EXTREMELY SENSITIVE!), political records, and who knows what else. They left the hard drive in an unsecured location, and didn’t realize it was gone for months—some say the data could have filled millions of books, and NARA admitted the material was “personally identifiable,” impacting thousands of White House staffers, visitors, and even one of Al Gore’s daughters. NARA actually had to offer a large ($50,000!) reward to try and get the information back. What else have they “lost”? How can Americans trust a system like this? There is no security at NARA. I want my documents back! Read here.
